{"tid":406293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳推出無人駕駛巴士","createTime":"2017-09-19T13:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T04:59:50.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43978451dd4e4590054d72c63cc4518f47771bd7","tid":406293,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:52:01.000Z","msg":"【深圳推出無人駕駛巴士】<br />\n【你搭唔搭？】<br />\n<br />\n深圳巴士集團表示，他們正在與國家智能運輸中心及華為公司合作，共同研發無人駕駛技術，預計今年10月底會在深圳南科大等地區試驗兩條無人駕駛路線。<br />\n【深圳巴士將全面智能化】<br />\n集團董事長余鋼稱，未來會推動巴士智能化，例如在巴士上配置人臉識別技術，監控司機行為和疲勞程度，確保安全駕駛。他們亦在巴士上提供微信掃碼支付和投訴功能。<br />\n<br />\n截至2017年8月底，深圳已總共有1019條巴士線，10279個八十站，16873輛巴士，其中有14825輛為純電動巴士。連同鐵路項目，深圳巴士集團的日均客運量達到1067萬人次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/1498534530291028\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fposts%2F1498534530291028&d=RwxKApIyLqjTLCqDI3HY%2Bmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e46de08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/posts/1498534530291028</a>"},{"pid":"01d3f67b88fd953d3c5ec8c4b0a1432919f36545","tid":406293,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"話唔定冇人好過有人"},{"pid":"d41673cd21e13d4f9d94424da447eb89b8e140b8","tid":406293,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T13:53:24.000Z","msg":"仲會唔會有人俾錢?"},{"pid":"090f45b1cf8c30fc3f104930a8fd000f56536af6","tid":406293,"uid":3698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲會唔會有人俾錢?</blockquote><br />\n直頭諗計成架車偷"},{"pid":"96536a875378e5502a19596713a23a8b7e0ac3fa","tid":406293,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:11:53.000Z","msg":"係車度打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個問題唔係敢唔敢坐<br />\n其實個真正問題係敢唔敢出街<br />\n無人揸, 撞死人, 無人要負責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f961fa4337406e41997e0d28806d9c9c5d96678","tid":406293,"uid":25822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"自動剎車都搞唔掂，仲玩自動駕駛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f44103fd278de1fcb6d3eaca0473e826c8b52cb4","tid":406293,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:04:44.000Z","msg":"RIP天佑中國"},{"pid":"3b88a0aa5e23974942efac406be8c1b9df9d5350","tid":406293,"uid":53223,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲會唔會有人俾錢?</blockquote><br />\n我去深圳搭巴士不知幾文明啦D人，大部分都係電動，企路邊等車唔洗好似香港咁噴到你一面都係。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d347a9da2c02265d94761eb445930b7fc037d2a","tid":406293,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係車度打劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個問題唔係敢唔敢坐<br />\n其實個真正問題係敢唔敢出街<br />\n無人揸, 撞死人, 無人要負責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公安咪捉你囉，而家係大陸犯法，一街都係天眼，走撚得甩就奇，尤其係深圳。"},{"pid":"dfe59423f884b3d4ed2a39ef2e0c8a73489331c1","tid":406293,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"中國地獄鬼國的軟件是使用中除蟲！"},{"pid":"32e0f6dd8e81ecc3b2e30afd98fbd4e30ff3ade8","tid":406293,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:16:33.000Z","msg":"真係對大陸野冇信心<br />\n<br />\n一陣架車出事, 明明係程式問題, 但係佢地話係路面 / 其他因素唔賠償"},{"pid":"b9534ad8fd536b039f4b6176bd0fe7853b54ee0f","tid":406293,"uid":104081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪